  "texts": [
    "Recent studies have highlighted the importance of faithful and project-specific feedback (Jia et al., 2024), as well as the potential of interactive feedback mechanisms (Jia et al., 2024).",
    "Moreover, empirical evidence has demonstrated the effectiveness of LLM-generated feedback on student outcomes in the writing domain (Meyer et al., 2024).",
    "In line with these findings, LEAP offers a platform that streamlines the creation of learning content and fosters interaction with a LLM, providing a promising solution for the provision of effective formative feedback.",
    "As new generative AI technologies continue to emerge, our work contributes to the ongoing discussion on the principle and technology sides of feedback modalities in different learning contexts (Stamper et al., 2024).",
    "By exploring the potential of LEAP in enhancing the learning experience, this paper aims to contribute to the theoretical and practical implications of LLM-based feedback systems, ultimately informing the development of more effective and personalized learning environments."
  ],
